title: How would you rate this home? Res Lease in Austin. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['POSITION PERFECT!', '\xa0\xa0This lovely home is just 10 minutes to downtown offering comfort and convenience!', 'Step inside to 2 spacious living areas, 2 dining areas, an open kitchen, and nicely sized bedrooms.', 'The vaulted ceiling\xa0adds a dramatic tone to the living area, and the wood burning fire place creates an inviting atmosphere.', 'The primary suite features access to the back yard covered patio, a separate shower and tub, and ample closet space.', "The huge yard provides plenty of shade from the summer sun, and you'll love relaxing on the large covered back porch.", "You'll also love the oversized garage, separate laundry room with utility sink, fresh exterior paint, and not a stitch of carpet anywhere!", 'The incredible community amenities include pools, parks, trails, sport courts, greenbelt access, and playgrounds.', "Located just off of Southwest Parkway and Mopac, you're just a stone's throw away from Sunset Valley, Downtown, Barton Creek Greenbelt, and so much more.", 'Put this gem on your MUST SEE LIST', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 4931010)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Macklin Cahill, Legacy Oak Realty']
